  <body id="msgFeedSummaryBody" selected="false">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>With <a href="http://news.cnet.com/8301-1023_3-57620423-93/outage-hits-google-talk-hangouts/">Hangouts being offline right now</a>, it might be a good opportunity to catch up on some of the exciting, free and open alternatives:</p>
<ul><li><a href="http://danielpocock.com/jitmeet-webrtc-free-communications-takes-another-big-jump">the Jitsi team have produced a pure browser-based video conferencing solution called JitMeet</a></li>
<li><a href="http://danielpocock.com/debian-sip-without-reading-the-manual">Debian Developers have access to the <b>rtc.debian.org</b> SIP service</a> which can receive calls from non-DD friends through <a href="https://freephonebox.net">freePhoneBox.net</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.drucall.org">the DruCall project</a> for Drupal makes it really easy to host your own WebRTC service in a Drupal site</li>
<li><a href="http://jscommunicator.org">JSCommunicator</a> lets just about any other site go WebRTC with little more than some cut and paste</li>
</ul></div></div></div>
